These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  lawyer, musician, chef, photographer, security-guard, writer, engineer
City: miami, rome, nizza, boston, colone, new-york, london
House: craftsman, victorian, tower, gothic-revival, art-deco, palace, wooden
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, february, october, june, september, december, november
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
 2. the art-deco house is the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the tower house##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 6. the musician is the tower house##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person traveling to new-york##2
 9. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the chef is in the middle##1
11. the craftsman house is the security-guard##1
12. the security-guard is the person who's birthday is in january##1
13. the lawyer is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
14. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in october##1
15. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
16. the musician is on the left of the writer##1
17. the palace house is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
18. the engineer is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
19. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Job      | musician  | writer        | security-guard | chef      | photographer     | lawyer      | engineer     |
| City   | rome | boston         | london   | miami | new-york    | colone | nizza |
| House         | tower | art-deco | craftsman | victorian | wooden  | palace  | gothic-revival    |
| Birthday     | september  | december         | january     | february    | october | june     | november     |

