 7. the indian is the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person playing billiard is between the person playing whist and the malaysian##2
11. the person playing backgammon is the argentine##1
12. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
13. the person playing snooker is between the malaysian and the person playing scrabble##2
14. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
15. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
16. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
17. the australian is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
18. the canadian is on the left of the russian##1
19. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
20. the russian is between the person who's sport is rowing and the canadian##2

