There 7 different types of food: eggplant, cranberry, artichoke, pepper, avocado, lemon, broccoli
7 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, guinea-pig, horse, bird, cat, turtle
 1. the owner of the cat is the montecristo-smoker##1
