 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the japanese is on the far left##1
 6. the malaysian is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the italian is on the left of the british##1
 8. the malaysian is in the middle##1
 9. the brazilian is the owner of the cat##1
10. the person eating pepper is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
11. the owner of the horse is the person eating lemon##1
12. the brazilian is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
13. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
14. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the polish##1
15. the argentine is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
16. the dannemann-smoker is the person eating artichoke##1
17. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
18. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the fish##2
